                <a class="link" href="https://www.instagram.com/lakterka/"><img class="icon" src="/images/icons/icons8-ig--48.png" alt="instagram-icon"></a>    
            </div>
                © 2023 Tereza Melichar | Icons by <a class="link" href="https://icons8.com/">icons8</a>.
